{"id":232295240,"title":"關於寶可夢大師準備優化","content":"http://i.imgur.com/4UIHDZc.jpg\n 　　《Pokemon Master》製作人佐佐木悠首先感謝一眾玩家一個月來一直支持遊戲，並向玩家就遊戲的三大問題作出道歉，包括遊戲中出現很多 BUG 以及營運的應對速度緩慢、對遊戲的內容量和等級評估不足、收集到玩家意見以及情報發布花的時間太長等。 \n\n不得不說一開始看到這款手遊的時候小弟真的覺得非常興奮，畢竟有太多喜歡的人物沒有在遊戲中出現過，所以這作品算是有幫我小小的圓夢到，不過可惜的是進入比較農的階段後就慢慢失去樂趣了，一方面是獎勵真的太不吸引人了，另一方面是小弟的手機已經年紀很大了....每次掛多人不到半小時都熱到快要可以煎蛋了OAO，所以希望這次優化可以把一些網友已經提出來的缺點都改進再看看要不要回去繼續玩了QQ\n\n文章來源： \nhttps://game.kikinote.net/12302","excerpt":"《Pokemon Master》製作人佐佐木悠首先感謝一眾玩家一個月來一直支持遊戲，並向玩家就遊戲的三大問題作出道歉，包括遊戲中出現很多 BUG 以及營運的應對速度緩慢、對遊戲的內容量和等級評估不足、","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"99049f5e-bb3d-420f-b708-52c384359952","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-14T07:44:21.233Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-14T07:44:21.233Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["寶可夢大師"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"寶可夢","forumAlias":"pokemon","school":"中臺科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/4UIHDZc.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"a1ad91b0-a7a6-49b5-a6fa-a414d1bb7bdd","url":"https://i.imgur.com/4UIHDZcl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/4UIHDZcl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/4UIHDZcl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-14T07:44:21.233Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-14T07:44:21.233Z"},{"id":"a1ad91b0-a7a6-49b5-a6fa-a414d1bb7bdd","url":"http://i.imgur.com/4UIHDZc.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/4UIHDZc","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/4UIHDZcl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-14T07:44:21.233Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-14T07:44:21.233Z"}],"postAvatar":""}